FBIS4-6186 "dreas075_d_94004" FBIS-EAS-94-075 Daily Report 17 Apr 1994 South Korea Ministry on Issue of `Discontinuing' Team Spirit Ministry on Issue of `Discontinuing' Team Spirit SK1704022394 Seoul CHOSON ILBO in Korean 17 Apr 94 p 2 SK1704022394 Seoul CHOSON ILBO Korean BFN [By Yu Yong-won] [Text] The ROK Defense Ministry stated on 16 April that it would consider discontinuing the Team Spirit exercise if North Korea accepts [suyong] additional inspections from the International Atomic Energy Agency and if progress is made in resolving the nuclear issue. The Defense Ministry reportedly mapped out this plan because the government abandoned the plan on the exchange of special envoys.
